---
// Sección BENEFITS
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-gray-950">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- Header mejorado -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span
                class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-red-900/30 border border-red-500/20 rounded-full text-red-300 text-sm font-semibold mb-4"
            >
                Ventajas Competitivas
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                Por Qué Nuestros Compresores<span class="text-red-500">
                    Superan</span
                > a la Competencia
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Tecnología de vanguardia diseñada para maximizar su
                productividad y minimizar sus costos
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Grid de ventajas -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Ventaja 1 - Tecnología -->
            <div class="relative group">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        Tecnología Rotativa de Flujo Estable
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Compresión eficiente con <span
                            class="text-red-300 font-semibold"
                            >flujo de aire constante</span
                        > y sin pulsaciones. Elimine las fluctuaciones que dañan sus
                        equipos sensibles.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Ventaja 2 - Mantenimiento -->
            <div class="relative group">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        Mantenimiento Simplificado
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Diseño intuitivo que reduce el tiempo de mantenimiento
                        hasta un <span class="text-red-300 font-semibold"
                            >60%</span
                        >. Accesos estratégicos y componentes modulares para
                        intervenciones rápidas.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Ventaja 3 - Durabilidad -->
            <div class="relative group">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        Construcción Premium para Larga Vida Útil
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Componentes de grado industrial con <span
                            class="text-red-300 font-semibold"
                            >garantía extendida</span
                        >. Diseñados para operar más de 50,000 horas sin pérdida
                        de eficiencia.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Ventaja 4 - Ahorro Energético -->
            <div class="relative group">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        Hasta 45% de Ahorro Energético
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Sistema inteligente que ajusta el consumo en tiempo
                        real.
                        <span class="text-red-300 font-semibold"
                            >Recupere su inversión en menos de 18 meses</span
                        > solo con el ahorro en electricidad.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Ventaja 5 - Operación 24/7 -->
            <div class="relative group">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        Operación Continua 24/7
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Diseñados para producción ininterrumpida.
                        <span class="text-red-300 font-semibold"
                            >Funcionamiento garantizado</span
                        > bajo las condiciones más demandantes sin pérdida de rendimiento.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Ventaja 6 - Resistencia Térmica -->
            <div class="relative group">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent rounded-2xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-300 h-full"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M17.293 13.293A8 8 0 016.707 2.707a8.001 8.001 0 1010.586 10.586z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        Resistencia Térmica Extrema
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Operación estable hasta <span
                            class="text-red-300 font-semibold"
                            >46°C ambiente</span
                        >. Sistema de enfriamiento avanzado que mantiene la
                        eficiencia en las condiciones más adversas.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Mejorado -->
        <div class="mt-20 text-center">
            <div
                class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800/50 to-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 rounded-2xl p-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
            >
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                    ¿Listo para Transformar su Productividad?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Un asesor especializado analizará su operación actual y le
                    mostrará <span class="text-red-300 font-semibold"
                        >exactamente cuánto puede ahorrar</span
                    > con nuestros sistemas.
                </p>

                <a
                    href="https://wa.me/1234567890?text=Hola!%20He%20visto%20las%20ventajas%20de%20sus%20compresores%20y%20quiero%20saber%20exactamente%20cuánto%20podría%20ahorrar%20en%20mi%20operación%20actual."
                    target="_blank"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-10 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 hover:from-red-700 hover:to-red-800 text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl shadow-red-500/25 border border-red-500/30 group"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-7 h-7 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Quiero Saber Exactamente Cuánto Puedo Ahorrar</span>
                </a>

                <p
                    class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-4 h-4 text-red-400"
                        fill="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                    Consulta confidencial • Sin compromiso • Respuesta en 15 minutos
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
